### Functional Tests
- [x] **CLI Download**: Isolated and verified core engine (Fixed hang).
- [x] **FastAPI Health**: `127.0.0.1:8080/api/health` returns `200 OK`.
- [x] **PWA Manifest**: Validated share sheet configuration.
- [x] **TUI Integration**: Footer now dynamically displays the Webport URL.

## Next Steps
- Open `zget-server` in a background screen or systemd service on your Mac.
- Access the IP provided in the TUI footer on your phone to install the PWA.
